description: Going, going… soon to be gone! Check out this two-bedroom two full bath, 1,155 square foot, guard gated condo with all appliances. Easy access to the Las Vegas Strip and sports venues and all that they offer! This turnkey, top floor unit has a large balcony overlooking one of multiple pools, and tennis courts at this location. Parking includes: Open parking, assigned covered / gated parking, and its own private one car attached garage. This unit in Park Avenue offers a combination of convenience, amenities, and security, making it a highly desirable option for buyers. The proximity to the Las Vegas Strip is a major selling point, as it provides easy access to the city's vibrant entertainment scene while still offering a comfortable living environment.
